text: Tuchenbach is a municipality in Fürth in Bavaria in Germany. ==Geography== Tuchenbach is about 20 Kilometer west of Nuremberg. The closest villages are Obermichelbach, Veitsbronn, Puschendorf and the town of Herzogenaurach. The altitude is 345 Meters. The area of Tuchenbach is 6.50 km2 ==References== ==Other websites== * http://www.tuchenbach.de/ * http://www.sportfreunde- tuchenbach.de/ * http://www.tc-tuchenbach.de/ Category:Fürth (district)
